Transform a vector/univariate time series in an hankel matrix

Source: R/hankel_matrix.R
hankel_matrix.Rd

Transform a vector/univariate time series in an hankel matrix

Usage

hankel_matrix(x, L)

Arguments

x

A vector or a time series

L

A number.

Value

An hankel matrix.

Examples

x <- datasets::AirPassengers
L <- 12
hankel_matrix(x, L)
